{"tid":2409082,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中資泰禾人壽有燶味 罕有停收新保單3個月 員工憂公司爆煲","createTime":"2021-02-15T13:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T16:53:31.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"112b7430eb34771a7af863675da4754e3b486036","tid":2409082,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4rWKrdC7G08WeGFPE9Xjs5b7Hd8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OM3VSIDWANAPBOJBDSITFNAYWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4rWKrdC7G08WeGFPE9Xjs5b7Hd8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOM3VSIDWANAPBOJBDSITFNAYWY.jpg&h=3f619562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地上市民企泰禾集團財務危機未解決，姊妹公司泰禾投資旗下本港泰禾人壽亦有「燶味」。本報獲悉，<span class=\"red\">泰禾於本周一（2月8日）起已經暫停所有新業務，為期3個月</span>，無論是內部員工或是客戶，都擔心公司在農曆新年假期，年關難過瀕爆煲。<br />\n<br />\n據泰禾人壽內部員工透露，公司所有銷售渠道已於周一起暫停接收新業務，稱是與新業務夥伴「商談到了一個關鍵時刻」之故，但令她質疑的是公司償付比率疑似超標，所以暫停賣保單，「本身公司前排已經裁員幾十人，降低經營成本」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有關新業務將會暫停3個月，部份代理人於上周六、日簽回來的保單，亦要辦理退款手續。現時內部人心惶惶，擔憂是爆煲先兆。<br />\n<br />\n本報致電客戶服務中心，職員承認泰禾人壽現時拒絕接收新生意，所有保單暫停申請，原因是「檢視策略，定未來方針」，而時間約為3個月內。至於是檢視甚麼策略，職員語塞，僅指是為一些長遠目標做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">發言人：策略性檢討</span></strong><br />\n泰禾人壽發言人回覆本報時確認暫停接收新保單3個月，稱正就未來發展方向及長遠目標進行策略性檢討，並繼續積極與潛在投資者商討，注入新元素以及更多資源，協助公司業務進一步拓展。<br />\n<br />\n保監局發言人不評論個別保險公司的商業決定。該局一直與所有獲授權保險公司保持溝通，以了解它們的業務運作及確保其遵守有關的規管要求，並密切監察其償付準備金水平，以保障投保人的利益。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cqQEb9qBPJ8XZNDx9atWnBRFiRs=/802x522/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QDCCTG2V4555ANF3FDZZPGIZCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcqQEb9qBPJ8XZNDx9atWnBRFiRs%3D%2F802x522%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQDCCTG2V4555ANF3FDZZPGIZCY.jpg&h=a125639c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大新銀行為泰禾人壽產品的銷售方，基於雙方協議，大新不能銷售其他公司壽險產品（年金公司例外），意味有機會影響佣金收入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">平保傳擬78億競購泰禾人壽</span></strong><br />\n事實上，內部通訊有提到泰禾人壽停止新生意與「新業務夥伴」有關，疑似將原因推向賣盤。市場多次傳出泰禾投資有意出售旗下泰禾人壽，《彭博》早前引述知情人士稱，平保（2318）與陽光保險等公司均有意競購，該交易或可籌集逾10億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210211/Q4DQ55IZXBAJZEGNQ5UM3QWAGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210211%2FQ4DQ55IZXBAJZEGNQ5UM3QWAGE%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=6a8723e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210211%2FQ4DQ55IZXBAJZEGNQ5UM3QWAGE%2F&h=c3047e63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210211/Q4DQ55IZXBAJZEGNQ5UM3QWAGE/</a><br />\nRead More:<br />\n國金89樓｜泰禾客戶要幫保監局開年（程總裁）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210214/UETAKRBJLVHURAO7P2SMEJS45I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210214%2FUETAKRBJLVHURAO7P2SMEJS45I%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=3e91de9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210214%2FUETAKRBJLVHURAO7P2SMEJS45I%2F&h=77372822\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210214/UETAKRBJLVHURAO7P2SMEJS45I/</a>"},{"pid":"ba06485c5a51ffe907de1149f7e7bc663540a215","tid":2409082,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"比連登仔燈一燈就唔會爆架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dbef7ca9d523ed866ea38b2abec8bb43d0f5ff","tid":2409082,"uid":63779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過。"},{"pid":"4e5cddd394d19a74bf45a6c9edb73554468738c1","tid":2409082,"uid":169116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:23:06.000Z","msg":"前名大新人壽"},{"pid":"81df1ed509bd257153a4ccfcb9518f48b90eba4a","tid":2409082,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:23:07.000Z","msg":"係咪古巨基代言果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbf9aa4603242776868745834d481791ada2394","tid":2409082,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81df1ed509bd257153a4ccfcb9518f48b90eba4a","tid":2409082,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:23:07.000Z","msg":"係咪古巨基代言果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:35:31.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"a405d1006d0e3fe82c84c9c129d3e7ffbd0a5e38","tid":2409082,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T16:53:31.000Z","msg":"呢間野啲whole life plan簡直係全宇宙最垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}